@startuml state-badge-progress
title Badge Progress State Machine

[*] --> Locked

state Locked {
}

state InProgress {
}

state Earned {
}

state Displayed {
}

Locked --> InProgress : First qualifying\naction recorded
Locked --> Earned : Single-action badge\n(e.g., FIRST_PLAY)\nthreshold = 1

InProgress --> InProgress : Progress incremented /\nupdate progress counter
InProgress --> Earned : Threshold met /\naward badge,\nshow celebration

Earned --> Displayed : Celebration dismissed /\nbadge visible in profile

note right of InProgress
  Progress is tracked silently.
  No pressure or countdown
  is shown to the child.
  Badges are a surprise reward.
end note

note right of Displayed
  Badges remain permanently
  in the child's profile.
  They cannot be revoked.
end note

@enduml
